  The DFT of h(0, ·):
  ĥ(0, 0) = h₀ = d(a+b)
  ĥ(0, k) = -(a+b)/2 - (a-b)/2 × (k/p) × i√p    for k ≠ 0

  p=7: α = (a+b)/2 = 9/2, β = (a-b)/2 = -7/2
